	<div class="view-default job" itemscope="null" itemtype="http://schema.org/JobPosting">

        <div class="component-page-intro clearfix page-background-color">

				<div class="centered">
				
			<div class="wrapper">
				<div class="whitespace-small"></div>
									<h2 itemprop="name">Take ownership of your career</h2>
								<p class="bodytext">We believe that everyone should write their own story and design a career that suits them. We promise to provide you with the tools and coaching so that you can rise as fast as your work and achievements allow.</p>

				
								<div class="whitespace-small"></div>
			</div>

			
				</div>
		
	</div>
		<div class="centered">
            <div class="row">

                <div class="left col-md-8 col-sm-7">
                    <div class="content">
                        <div class="whitespace-large"></div>
						
						<div class="wrapper">

							<h1 class="h2" itemprop="title">Senior Data Scientist</h1>
                            <div class="whitespace-small"></div>

                            
                            <p class="h3" itemprop="jobLocation">Location: New York NY</p>

	                        <div class="bodytext" itemprop="description">
	                        	<h3>
LET’S TALK ABOUT YOU</h3>
<p>
You
 want to Own Your Career. You’re serious about rising as far and as fast
 as your work and achievements can take you. And you’re ready to write 
the next chapter of your career story: a challenging
 and rewarding role as a Senior Data Scientist</p>
<h3>
A WORD ABOUT US</h3>
<p>
Capco – Forming the Future of Finance</p>
<p>
Capco
 is a distinctly and positively different place to work. Much more than 
consultants, we are active participants in the global financial services
 industry. Our passionate business and technology
 professionals enjoy a unique environment where they are actively 
encouraged to apply intellect, innovation, experience and teamwork. We 
are dedicated to fully supporting our world class clients as they 
respond to challenges and opportunities in the financial
 services space. Experience Capco for yourself at <a href="http://capco.com">capco.com</a></p>
<h3>
LET’S GET DOWN TO BUSINESS</h3>
<p>Capco is looking for Senior Data Scientists. The ideal candidate will
Manage
 a team of data scientists and work with business sponsors and technical
 teams to successfully design, develop and implement analytical 
solutions</p>
<p>
–      
Build
 customer profiling and predictive models utilizing both traditional 
statistical methods (Generalized Linear Models, Mixed Effects Models, 
Ridge,
 Lasso, etc.) and modern machine learning techniques (Gradient Boosted 
Trees, Random Forests, Kernel methods, Deep Learning, etc.)</p>
<p>
–      
Extract, clean, and manipulate large datasets (structured and unstructured) for model building in Hadoop environment</p>
<p>
 </p>
<p>
You will also be:</p>
<p>
Fitting
 that description, you will also need to be Supremely Personally 
Motivated to work in a team where clients become colleagues too.</p>
<h3>
SHOW US WHAT YOU’VE GOT</h3>
<p>
–      
Very strong background in one or more computational areas (Computer Science, Statistics, Economics, Physics)</p>
<p>
–      
At least 4 years proven experience with multiple modeling techniques</p>
<p>
–      
Exceptional programming skills in one or more platforms, preferably Python, R, or SAS</p>
<p>
–      
Exceptional
 skills in Apache Hadoop and related toolset (MapR, HDFS, Sqoop, YARN, 
Spark, etc), Java and ElasticSearch is nice to have</p>
<p>
–      
Masters Degree (Preferably a PhD)</p>
<p>
–      
Experience working with clients in the Financial Services industry
</p>
<p>
–      
Experience working in Big Data (Hadoop) environment</p>
<p>
–      
The drive to deliver on commitments and an openness to new ideas</p>
<p>
 </p>
<p>
100% travel to client site may be required</p>
<p>
Fitting that description, you will also need to be Supremely Personally Motivated to</p>
<p>
work in a team where clients become colleagues too.</p>
<h3>
NOW TAKE THE NEXT STEP</h3>

If you’re looking forward to progressing your career with us, then we’re looking forward to receiving your application. <br/>
							</div>
                            
